{"title":"支援麦收","authors":["傅占元"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":6,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"支援麦收"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"郑州热电厂工人　傅占元"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月儿清又亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照在麦地上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦棵黄澄澄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"微风卷细浪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手握快镰刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"镰刀闪银光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦梗沙沙响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦倒一行行。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比谁割的快，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比谁有力量，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片人影动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全是工人装……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社姐妹们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"端茶到身旁："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“工人大哥呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"淡水润润嗓”……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一碗白开水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"友谊怎么量？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜过红玫酒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"强似甜蜜糖……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一口喝个尽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碗底朝天上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"割到晨乌啼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满脸红霞光……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}